  <li><span class="step-num">02</span><div><strong>Prioritization — Start with a reminder system.</strong> The starting point with the least technical complexity and highest risk reduction.</div></li>
  <li><span class="step-num">03</span><div><strong>Implementation — Integrate with your existing calendar and email system.</strong> It's possible to start automating via Google Workspace or Microsoft 365 without installing separate software.</div></li>
